      "content": "thanks. i like the part about it being a \"moral imperative.\" i want to make the section where i address the counter-arguments even stronger. how should i frame the arguments from people who support meritocracy? i want to show why their view is basically just a way to justify keeping the status quo and ignoring systemic issues.",
